                <![CDATA[<p>羅馬在今天凌晨的意甲比賽前，全員身穿帶有自己簽名的第二客場入場。（這波帶貨真硬）</p><p><img data-width="1080" data-height="1350" src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/07/BC/rBUBsmUaP5KAfy2rAAJ39N2y3sU604.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p><img data-width="1080" data-height="1349" src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/0B/DA/rBUC6GUaP5SAMXbQAAKyb5D4lfI224.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p><img data-width="1080" data-height="1350" src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/07/BC/rBUBsmUaP5aANCipAAKM76L_pfU124.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p><img data-width="1080" data-height="1350" src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/0B/DA/rBUC6GUaP5iAMQP8AALkFuc6Cl8708.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p><img data-width="1332" data-height="2000" src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/07/BC/rBUBsmUaP5qAXk7jAAZRyBQW5Uw118.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p><img data-width="1333" data-height="2000" src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/0B/DA/rBUC6GUaP5yASIp1AAXt4ouSNjg982.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p>]]>
